  <brief_title>Heat Acclimation, Hand Cooling Efficacy, and Adaptation Maintenance.</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect of Heat Acclimation on Repeated Bouts of Strenuous Heat Stress, Hand Cooling Efficacy, and the Maintenance Thereof.</official_title>
